data.description: Nicely updated home with NO HOA. Private yard with "tree fence" provides lots of privacy and feels like you are in the secret garden. Spacious kitchen is inviting and has plenty of counter space, all appliances in kitchen included. Nice dining area, separate laundry area with lots of storage and washer and dryer included. Good size living room with decorative and fully functioning electric stove. Two good size bedrooms adjoins the bathroom which is fully remodeled with nice walk-in tile shower. Great outdoor space with patio areas in the front and in the back. Detached garage is a great workshop, plus 2 other storage sheds that stay. Back yard is ready for your creativity for you to finish it how you like. You will love this cute and cozy home- call for your private showing today!
